    <item>
      <title>南非计划新的税收措施和电动汽车制造激励措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/south-africa-plans-new-tax-measures-ev-manufacturing-incentives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国家财政部公布了一系列措施，增加收入 150 亿兰特（7.93 亿美元），以缓解眼前的财政压力，并计划对税收制度进行长期改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/south-africa-plans-new-tax-measures-ev-manufacturing-incentives</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 12:06:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰对俄罗斯声称占领桥头堡提出异议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/ukraine-clings-to-bridgehead-that-russia-claimed-to-have-seized</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰表示，在俄罗斯国防部长告诉总统弗拉基米尔·普京(Vladimir Putin)已被其军队占领后，乌克兰军队继续保卫第聂伯河南岸俄罗斯占领领土上的一小片土地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/ukraine-clings-to-bridgehead-that-russia-claimed-to-have-seized</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:18:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯禁止英国船只在其水域捕鱼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/russia-bans-uk-ships-from-fishing-in-its-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国家杜马禁止英国船只在俄罗斯北极水域和科拉半岛沿岸捕捞鳕鱼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/russia-bans-uk-ships-from-fishing-in-its-waters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:16:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国承诺为农民提供更多帮助以避免新的抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/france-pledges-more-help-for-farmers-to-stop-protests-reigniting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理加布里埃尔·阿塔尔承诺将加强一项旨在确保农民获得公平价格的法律以及其他措施，因为他寻求兑现承诺，在数周的全国抗议活动后解决农民的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/france-pledges-more-help-for-farmers-to-stop-protests-reigniting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
